Subject: drm/amd/display: Prevent crash when disable stream
Git-commit: 72d72e8fddbcd6c98e1b02d32cf6f2b04e10bd1c
Patch-mainline: v6.9-rc2
References: jsc#PED-9898 jsc#PED-10191 jsc#PED-10197 jsc#PED-10226 jsc#PED-10237 jsc#PED-10340 jsc#PED-10852 jsc#PED-11022 CVE-2024-35799 bsc#1224740
